# Automatically load Nix development environment when entering this directory
#
# Setup instructions:
# 1. Install direnv:
#    - macOS: brew install direnv
#    - NixOS: add 'direnv' to environment.systemPackages
#    - Or: nix-env -iA nixpkgs.direnv
#
# 2. Add to your shell config (~/.zshrc or ~/.bashrc):
#    eval "$(direnv hook zsh)"  # for zsh
#    eval "$(direnv hook bash)" # for bash
#
# 3. Allow this .envrc:
#    direnv allow
#
# Then, whenever you cd into grimoire/, the Nix environment automatically loads!

use flake

# Optional: Watch additional files for changes
# watch_file flake.nix
# watch_file flake.lock
